The body that was used to fulfill Passover

01:04:44.425 --> 01:04:46.865
was entirely disposable.

01:04:47.326 --> 01:04:49.827
It's the soul that occupied it that made

01:04:49.867 --> 01:04:54.447
that body represent the Son of God and

01:04:54.487 --> 01:04:56.009
to fulfill Passover.

01:04:56.481 --> 01:04:57.021
Pesach.

01:04:57.782 --> 01:05:00.244
But it was Dowd's soul who took the

01:05:00.304 --> 01:05:02.867
guilt of every covenant member in sheowl

01:05:02.947 --> 01:05:04.369
on Matsah to deposit it there,

01:05:04.809 --> 01:05:05.789
never to be seen again.

01:05:06.690 --> 01:05:07.992
All of this was accomplished through

01:05:08.012 --> 01:05:09.833
Dowd's Nepesh, his soul.

01:05:10.132 --> 01:05:11.875
And it is Dowd's soul that will be

01:05:12.614 --> 01:05:15.818
put into another body to come back and

01:05:15.898 --> 01:05:18.300
is third of three lives as our king

01:05:19.681 --> 01:05:20.422
on Yom Kipurym.

01:05:21.583 --> 01:05:22.605
And year six thousand, Yah,

01:05:22.644 --> 01:05:23.585
twenty thirty three.

01:05:23.967 --> 01:05:26.550
It was through his soul.

01:05:27.210 --> 01:05:28.231
Souls matter.

01:05:28.512 --> 01:05:29.233
Bodies don't.

01:05:29.833 --> 01:05:33.818
This whole notion of of God was a

01:05:34.059 --> 01:05:37.061
physical man is so utterly absurd.

01:05:37.362 --> 01:05:38.264
God is not a man.

01:05:39.722 --> 01:05:42.244
All of God won't fit into the entire

01:05:42.463 --> 01:05:45.184
universe with two trillion galaxies.

01:05:45.284 --> 01:05:47.487
It won't fit into all of the galaxies,

01:05:47.547 --> 01:05:48.827
much less one galaxy,

01:05:49.148 --> 01:05:51.369
much less one solar system within one

01:05:51.409 --> 01:05:51.909
galaxy,

01:05:52.208 --> 01:05:54.391
much less on one planet within one solar

01:05:54.451 --> 01:05:56.331
system, much less in one man.

01:05:57.831 --> 01:05:58.873
God is seven-dimensional.

01:05:58.893 --> 01:05:59.753
We're three-dimensional.

01:06:00.134 --> 01:06:00.793
It doesn't work.

01:06:01.795 --> 01:06:02.755
God is not a man.

01:06:04.096 --> 01:06:05.476
Men cannot kill God.

01:06:06.657 --> 01:06:09.157
and bodily resurrection is the stuff of

01:06:09.177 --> 01:06:09.898
the Egyptians.

01:06:10.858 --> 01:06:13.378
How'd it work out for them?

01:06:13.478 --> 01:06:14.639
It's utterly stupid.

01:06:14.838 --> 01:06:15.880
It's counterproductive.

01:06:16.219 --> 01:06:17.539
It's the soul that matters.

01:06:17.800 --> 01:06:21.420
That's why this says, through my soul.

01:06:22.880 --> 01:06:25.161
And then he laments because he should.

01:06:26.101 --> 01:06:28.561
He volunteered to make this sacrifice,

01:06:29.641 --> 01:06:31.521
being crucified by the Romans in

01:06:31.561 --> 01:06:33.682
thirty-three CE on Passover,

01:06:34.043 --> 01:06:35.123
going into hell,

01:06:36.206 --> 01:06:38.688
to remove our guilt on Matsah,

01:06:39.449 --> 01:06:40.949
depositing it where it would never be seen

01:06:41.010 --> 01:06:41.351
again.

01:06:41.891 --> 01:06:44.472
And then as the Bakowr, the firstborn son,

01:06:44.594 --> 01:06:47.135
fulfilling Bikuwrym, firstborn children.

01:06:48.876 --> 01:06:49.657
All as he said,

01:06:49.777 --> 01:06:51.679
exactly when he said he would do so,

01:06:52.099 --> 01:06:54.262
when he met with Daniel in five fifty

01:06:54.282 --> 01:06:55.023
five BCE.

01:06:56.123 --> 01:06:56.244
Yeah,

01:06:56.284 --> 01:06:58.485
I know it because I was there and

01:06:58.545 --> 01:06:59.887
I know when he fulfilled it because I

01:06:59.907 --> 01:07:00.628
was there again.

01:07:02.369 --> 01:07:03.849
And I know when he learned that he

01:07:03.889 --> 01:07:06.490
would fulfill it because I was there also,

01:07:07.391 --> 01:07:08.251
all three times.

01:07:10.271 --> 01:07:11.773
You don't think so, I don't really care.

01:07:12.873 --> 01:07:13.413
I know so.

01:07:14.554 --> 01:07:15.114
It's evident.

01:07:16.074 --> 01:07:18.295
Just as it is evident that Dowd did

01:07:18.655 --> 01:07:19.494
all of these things.

01:07:19.815 --> 01:07:21.996
And yet he is dissatisfied because he has

01:07:22.036 --> 01:07:22.817
been pushed away.

01:07:22.876 --> 01:07:24.097
He has been discarded.

01:07:24.697 --> 01:07:26.297
He has been disregarded.

01:07:27.764 --> 01:07:29.326
very heavy on his heart and in his

01:07:29.365 --> 01:07:32.166
thinking every day, all of the time.

01:07:33.047 --> 01:07:34.887
It's one thing to have decided that he

01:07:34.907 --> 01:07:36.387
would serve us in this way.

01:07:36.768 --> 01:07:38.849
It's another for us to spit on him,

01:07:39.489 --> 01:07:41.630
bury him, disregard him.

01:07:42.449 --> 01:07:45.050
You've been given the greatest gift in

01:07:45.210 --> 01:07:46.351
universal history,

01:07:46.891 --> 01:07:48.791
and you not only tossed it away,

01:07:49.331 --> 01:07:51.693
you stomped on it,

01:07:51.773 --> 01:07:54.434
and then you replaced it with a token.

01:07:56.257 --> 01:07:57.777
Christians, Jews.

01:07:59.559 --> 01:08:02.420
For what extent of time will the one

01:08:02.460 --> 01:08:04.621
who is an opposition to me be lifted

01:08:04.681 --> 01:08:06.121
up and exalted over me?

01:08:07.322 --> 01:08:10.704
Not just talking about Paul, about Sha'uwl.

01:08:11.324 --> 01:08:12.224
No.

01:08:13.226 --> 01:08:14.626
He's talking about the demon that

01:08:14.666 --> 01:08:18.127
possessed Sha'uwl, Satan.

01:08:18.927 --> 01:08:21.890
Why don't you read the last chapter of

01:08:21.989 --> 01:08:24.650
second Corinthians where Paul admits that

01:08:24.690 --> 01:08:25.872
he was demon possessed.

01:08:27.610 --> 01:08:30.573
It is Satan that has lifted himself up

01:08:30.932 --> 01:08:32.194
as Jesus Christ.

01:08:32.954 --> 01:08:34.275
It is Satan that is Allah.

01:08:34.615 --> 01:08:36.256
It is Satan that is Hashem.

01:08:36.596 --> 01:08:38.278
It is Satan that is the Lord God

01:08:38.318 --> 01:08:38.918
of religion.

01:08:39.639 --> 01:08:42.421
And they are all exalted over Dowd,

01:08:42.480 --> 01:08:44.762
who is the Son of God, our Savior,

01:08:45.103 --> 01:08:45.802
and Elyown,

01:08:46.224 --> 01:08:52.488
the very presence of God in our world.

01:08:52.507 --> 01:08:53.969
Very extension of God's hand.

01:08:55.871 --> 01:08:59.752
And yet the religious Jews and Gentiles

01:08:59.792 --> 01:09:03.574
alike have raised up the one who is

01:09:03.635 --> 01:09:04.895
the adversary,

01:09:05.935 --> 01:09:07.957
lifting him up and exalting him over

01:09:08.016 --> 01:09:11.439
Dowd.

01:09:11.458 --> 01:09:12.179
I'm going to stop there.

01:09:12.698 --> 01:09:14.199
We'll return to this passage.

01:09:14.399 --> 01:09:15.841
You can see I'm passionate about it.

01:09:16.801 --> 01:09:18.021
It's the answer for everything.

01:09:18.546 --> 01:09:20.007
I mean, here, just the thirteenth Psalm.

01:09:20.347 --> 01:09:21.569
You ever heard anybody talk to you about

01:09:21.609 --> 01:09:22.350
the thirteenth Psalm?

01:09:22.949 --> 01:09:24.251
Am I the only one who has made

01:09:24.310 --> 01:09:25.070
sense of it for you?

01:09:25.492 --> 01:09:26.752
Am I the only one who is compelling

01:09:26.792 --> 01:09:29.774
you to place it in your heart,

01:09:29.975 --> 01:09:30.734
in your mind,

01:09:32.195 --> 01:09:34.518
such that you can share this with others

01:09:34.557 --> 01:09:35.698
so that it guides your life,

01:09:35.719 --> 01:09:38.921
so that you have an appreciation for how

01:09:38.980 --> 01:09:40.442
essential this knowledge is?

01:09:42.042 --> 01:09:43.322
And for all those people that would

01:09:43.742 --> 01:09:46.502
besmirch this calling that I have on

01:09:46.542 --> 01:09:49.002
behalf of God to do this very thing,

01:09:49.463 --> 01:09:51.904
I want you to process this because no

01:09:52.104 --> 01:09:55.284
one knew it until I figured it out

01:09:55.944 --> 01:09:57.465
and began to share it with you and

01:09:57.545 --> 01:10:03.206
proved it over and over again.

01:10:03.265 --> 01:10:04.046
May Yahowah bless.

01:10:04.487 --> 01:10:07.006
It's been a pleasure being able to deliver

01:10:07.426 --> 01:10:09.347
this passionate message from you as the

01:10:10.287 --> 01:10:10.988
trade winds

01:10:12.511 --> 01:10:17.216
roar through the palm fronds and the waves

01:10:17.235 --> 01:10:19.818
of the ocean beneath my feet crash against

01:10:19.877 --> 01:10:22.420
the shore, from my home to yours.

01:10:23.121 --> 01:10:24.140
May Yah bless you all,

01:10:24.180 --> 01:10:25.582
and I look forward to being with you

01:10:25.603 --> 01:10:25.783
tomorrow.

01:10:25.802 --> 01:10:25.962
Good day.

01:10:25.983 --> 01:10:26.662
Hey there, thanks for tuning in.

01:10:26.703 --> 01:10:27.083
That was Fetch.

01:10:27.104 --> 01:10:28.064
Gotta run now.

01:10:28.145 --> 01:10:34.109
Catch Yah on our next podcast.